Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.17,0:11:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}（始皇帝）うぐ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}な…！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}下へ潰す力に\N後ろへ引く力を加えて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.72,0:11:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}強引に受け流させない！
