Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.58,0:13:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}あの技
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}承力天鳳を出すチャンスを
